com.cyberfront.crdt

Class CRDTManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.CRDTManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericCRDTManager, JsonManager

    public class CRDTManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The CRDTManager class is used to wrap a CRDT instance so as to interact with it. The intent of this class is to provide an interface to manage JSON documents with the CRDT types provided.
